{"tid":2489764,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［基情四射］小鮮肉所長被爆「偷情」人夫警員 正宮：一天大戰好幾回","createTime":"2021-04-15T06:58:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T07:22:39.000Z","uid":391580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7c759fecacc58f4e2f23e8d82e771b575c21ce1c","tid":2489764,"uid":391580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:58:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTLHM362paHFsgNFHEAGhYRojsu8SF9MjngJcCMCZ6vSc?filename=HNzNE8s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHNzNE8s.jpg&h=e5d3a325&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新北市警局C姓前所長（左）與K姓警員（右）傳出婚外同性戀情，K姓警員的妻子除了抓姦、提告，還上網爆料，控訴這位男所長搶走她的丈夫。（記者吳仁捷翻攝）<br />\n<br />\n〔記者吳仁捷／新北報導〕新北市警局一處警分駐所C姓前所長被控與同所K姓男警過從甚密，329青年節凌晨警員妻帶著徵信業者到兩人同居處抓姦，當時所長赤裸上身、男警衣著完整睡在一旁，妻子控告妨害婚姻及家庭罪；新北警方約談兩人，不正常感情交往部分，雖查無實證，但仍以不落實勤務將兩人分別記過、拔官、調職處分；但截至截稿為止，未獲該名所長回應。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，30歲C姓警官為前某分駐所巡官兼所長，警大80期畢業，40歲K姓警員為95年特考班；警員妻在臉書「靠北警察」中露骨指控「OO分駐所長掰彎人夫警員&hellip;&hellip;」、「1月起被所內同事發現，兩人在新蓋好的辦公室內眉來眼去、異常的肢體動作&hellip;&hellip;且多次兩人一前一後進出廁所&hellip;&hellip;大家實在想不出竟會發展出甲甲戀（男同性戀）」。<br />\n<br />\n警員妻還加碼爆料，「所長扮演零號、丈夫扮演一號，兩人另租炮房大戰」，甚至直稱所長為女子，還PO上跟監時，所長為丈夫整理領子親暱動作。<br />\n<br />\n警員透露，「C所長不但工作時藉故外出與『人夫』約會，甚至租套房同居，方便兩人偷情當炮房，所長為討好『人夫』，會在車上替他服務，常送小禮物討人夫歡心，熱戀時一天大戰好幾回，潤滑液兩三天就要補貨，大爆所長有位警界爸爸撐腰&hellip;但大家看不過去，挺身而出爆料」，還爆料警方為滅火，案發後3天就將該所長調至某分局交通組。<br />\n<br />\n警方證實，3月29日上午3時許，警員妻子報案稱其配偶（K員）與時任某所長婚外情、出示她聘請徵信業者跟監的資料，警方受理提告，分局並查辦、約談2名員警，立即依勤務中溜班（勤務不落實）、不正常感情交往部分，記過及拔官等處分；員警間因感情引發非議，雖屬私德領域，但造成警察形象受損，警方依法辦理，不護短、不庇縱查辦，維護警察形象。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZonHKCdYivHPtRLhtBf8Ws8i8mRaLxRta9orduudGAn3?filename=bsGz4Az.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbsGz4Az.jpg&h=f2240340&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nK姓警員妻子上網PO出C姓前所長（左）與K姓警員（右）合照，爆料兩人有同性婚外情。（記者吳仁捷翻攝）"},{"pid":"7d696990fcd0f2ab1eeb55648d38a04156fc0063","tid":2489764,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:00:23.000Z","msg":"好sweet想join<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03c2b7bcec3dcb8ba351b53033c2c0a6b509598d","tid":2489764,"uid":321789,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:02:28.000Z","msg":"新北1分"},{"pid":"0b73dcfd2edb24a03e8dd1b428bef1d3e77a7f26","tid":2489764,"uid":93784,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:03:53.000Z","msg":"你老公扮演一號咪算好囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1be68f89a92e8bb0073dd02d2899c5192b06740e","tid":2489764,"uid":310700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:10:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><em></em>"},{"pid":"e455b014a95a8e6cdaa1216cd4c7232e65ebb925","tid":2489764,"uid":8810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b73dcfd2edb24a03e8dd1b428bef1d3e77a7f26","tid":2489764,"uid":93784,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:03:53.000Z","msg":"你老公扮演一號咪算好囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:11:34.000Z","msg":"你諗清楚先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92d806ce93508fdf1abed4456c10ee01b8e3d08d","tid":2489764,"uid":49664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:12:57.000Z","msg":"噢  同所長搞直昇機"},{"pid":"5a5d243d60d47faff7d2f38d6a5236049e759a75","tid":2489764,"uid":324712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:13:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1238221e4ff8bd770bbe6893967ffb351c28498f","tid":2489764,"uid":73628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:17:12.000Z","msg":"正喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fafd12877a7e57cea96f4d56b0db2c1cd1ee3a5","tid":2489764,"uid":214644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:19:02.000Z","msg":"又新北<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"304155449ab218f97ab2de50788f840a42271d86","tid":2489764,"uid":49664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:22:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXSscwNTA5bC6PbUuM3aNcBqbWKypg1s49YwAHSSFJmKs?filename=qdPt9an.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqdPt9an.gif&h=ed59228a&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}